title: VA - Slap On That Great '70's B Side [2008] 3 CDs CLASSIC ROCK
description:
There was nothing wrong with the songs. Maybe they didn&#039;t fit in with the overall theme of the album they were intended for. Perhaps the album would have been too long if they had been included. (Remember, in the Seventies a vinyl record would only allow for about 40 minutes of music.) Or perhaps the artist in question simply wanted to record something special, a bonus if you like for their fans. Either way, some fantastic songs ended up on the flip side of the hit single ... and plenty of people listened ... and enjoyed what they heard. On this three disc set the humble B side is finally given the honour it deserved!
